Contact Button: Add a 'Contact Provider' button next to each service provider's listing. 
This button can initiate a phone call or open an email template, depending on the provided contact information.

Scheduling Integration: Once contact is made, provide an option for users to schedule an appointment with the service provider through your app's scheduling system.

Payment Automation: After the service is completed, prompt the user with an option to pay the service provider via Stripe. You can set up a payment confirmation and receipt system for transparency and record-keeping.

Feedback System: After payment, offer the user the chance to rate and review the service, which helps maintain quality and trust within your platform.